{
  "stem": "4570.3",
  "chunk_idx": 14,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Even if things improved in Prague, it was handmade.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "It looked very smart for, for skirts and jackets and things.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I was doing very well and-- but-- well, it didn't last very long, because three years later Czechoslovakia turned Communist.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I left everything and took a suitcase.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And with two friends-- one of Goldie's friends and my boyfriend at the time.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We went to a German family near the border.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And the borders were already closed.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And at night, again, like thieves in the night, the three of us were guided by the Germans across into Bavaria.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And it took us the whole night, because our guide lost the way.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And eventually, daylight came, and we saw a cow that is like a cocker spaniel in two colors.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Because in, in Prague, all cows are brown or black or something.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And in Bavaria the cows are in two or three colors.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we saw this cow, and we knew we are in Bavaria.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So we went onto the road and a Jeep came and picked us up and took us to a German camp, Regensburg.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we were I don't know how long in that camp.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "There wasn't-- they didn't have much food to give us.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "The Germans had no food.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "It's not that they wanted-- didn't want to give us food, but there was no food.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But very soon we went to Italy and the camp was called Bagnoli in Italy.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And that was lovely.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The ocean-- the first time in my life I saw the ocean and all the Italian good food.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Even if it was camp food, it was terrific, all that pasta.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I had a very good job in the camp.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I worked in the, in the X-ray department.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
